Package model

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
model.Appointment
public class Appointment
extends java.lang.Object
Methods for obtaining, adding, or removing appointments from the database. This method allows appointment data to be accessed. Using this method, an appointment can be created, modified, and deleted.
